    "nodemon": "^3.1.14"
  },
  "//overrides": [
    "glob was pinned to 11.0.2 — inside the vulnerable range 11.0.0-11.0.3",
    "(GHSA-5j98-mcp5-4vw2, high). Bumped to ^11.1.0.",
    "The js-yaml override is gone: it only existed because pm2 6 shipped the",
    "vulnerable <=4.1.1. pm2 7 depends on 4.3.0 directly, so the root cause is fixed.",
    "cross-spawn was a direct dependency that no source file imports — it existed",
    "only to pin the CVE-fixed 7.0.6 (it is transitive via exceljs > archiver >",
    "glob > foreground-child). An override is the correct way to express that."
  ],
  "overrides": {
    "minimatch": "^10.0.2",
    "whatwg-url": "^14.0.0",
    "glob": "^11.1.0",
    "rimraf": "6.0.1",
    "fast-csv": "5.0.2",
    "cross-spawn": "^7.0.6"
  }
}
